WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.999
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.999 --> 00:00:03.129
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.129 --> 00:00:05.213
Well, I have my sweetheart with me today.

00:00:05.213 --> 00:00:06.546
She's behind the camera.

00:00:06.546 --> 00:00:08.320
She helps me pray when I pray.

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:12.057
I said I miss her when she's not in here because I can feel her.

00:00:12.057 --> 00:00:15.280
We tug along together after being married for as long as we have.

00:00:15.527 --> 00:00:19.417
I just know, and it's a blessing when she's here.

00:00:19.771 --> 00:00:22.229
You know, yesterday was a heavy word.

00:00:22.229 --> 00:00:31.680
There were a lot of things when we were driving around, and the Lord was showing me so much that seemed to be a real Debbie Downer.

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:36.070
I mean, after it was over, I said, "Lord, that was heavy.

00:00:36.070 --> 00:00:37.619
" And I was carrying it.

00:00:37.619 --> 00:00:43.339
I told Braden when he was editing the video, I said, "My goodness, I hope I didn't come across cranky.

00:00:45.691 --> 00:00:47.560
" And he goes, "A little bit.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:55.470
" And I said, "Well, when I'm carrying something so heavy, I might come across kind of cranky, and I don't mean to, ladies and gentlemen.

00:00:55.470 --> 00:01:00.640
I want you to understand, I'm passionate about what the Lord shows me.

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:01.872
I'm passionate about it.

00:01:01.872 --> 00:01:05.904
I believe in it, and I know what the Lord is trying to warn His people about.

00:01:06.216 --> 00:01:19.600
I have such an urgency, and that urgency and the heaviness of what I have seen—because when you're seeing it, I describe it to you, but I've seen it literally, people falling down dead, things happening—it grieves you.

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:22.240
It's heavy.

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:36.912
And so I think sometimes the urgency of what I feel in my spirit comes across as cranky, and I apologize if it did, but I want you to understand it is very urgent.

00:01:36.912 --> 00:01:43.400
And I'm trying to get across that you need to listen.

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:59.884
You know, I called my elders like Sister Billye yesterday, and I told her, "This is what I'm seeing, and this is what the Lord's warning about, and I'm seeing these ministers die on the platform, and I want you to judge the words as an elder.

00:01:59.884 --> 00:02:01.999
I want you to listen to what I'm going to say.

00:02:01.999 --> 00:02:05.910
And if it doesn't line up in your spirit, if you feel that it's off too...

00:02:05.910 --> 00:02:13.420
" Because I don't want to be somebody leading people by the hundreds of thousands, millions of people on a weekly basis, that comes across as flaky.

00:02:13.420 --> 00:02:27.956
But as an elder that's been in the faith preaching and teaching people about Jesus for 80-some years plus, I just want you to listen to this and let your spirit hear it.

00:02:28.178 --> 00:02:32.434
And she goes, "You know, Brandon, I'll judge the words, and I'll pray over them.

00:02:34.069 --> 00:02:40.151
" And I appreciate somebody who has been in the Word for so long.

00:02:40.151 --> 00:02:42.329
I mean, she's my elder.

00:02:42.329 --> 00:02:46.510
And she prayed with me, she prayed for me, and just really uplifted me.

00:02:46.510 --> 00:02:47.566
We had a great conversation.

00:02:47.566 --> 00:02:51.600
And I want to tell you all, it's a real blessing to have somebody like that.

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:53.590
I never take it for granted.

00:02:53.590 --> 00:03:06.569
It's a true blessing to be able to talk to somebody who is a seasoned minister that teaches about end times, teaches about prayer, teaches about eschatology, all the great stuff, and is accurate about things.

00:03:07.229 --> 00:03:15.257
And I give God praise for that opportunity to be able to talk to somebody that's not flaky, you know, that was around Brother Hagin, that was around John G.

00:03:15.257 --> 00:03:17.566
Lake's daughter and all the greats.

00:03:22.263 --> 00:03:24.800
I mean, seriously, it's amazing.

00:03:24.800 --> 00:03:32.679
So that being said, this is her praying over it and telling me basically she feels I'm on the right road.

00:03:32.679 --> 00:03:40.137
And she asked me, "What do you feel about the mega preacher that you saw being shot on the stage?

00:03:40.137 --> 00:03:47.480
There were two preachers, and they were trying to bring fear for people not wanting to go into the revival.

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:58.900
" And instantaneously, I said the Lord said, "Pray for this man that it does not take place.

00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:04.389
" Now, the exposing of the church in California, we pray for the church in California.

00:04:04.389 --> 00:04:10.449
But the bottom line is that God told me, "Brandon, judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:04:10.449 --> 00:04:13.280
And I'm cleaning up My church right now.

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:20.160
And many ministers that you see behind pulpits in the days ahead will not be there.

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:29.109
I'm raising up new Davids, new voices with different influence in these end times because the time is short.

00:04:29.109 --> 00:04:30.848
" He said, "I'm going to pour out...

00:04:31.264 --> 00:04:34.423
this is a different mantle that we've never seen before.

00:04:34.423 --> 00:04:36.479
" Like we've seen the John G.

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:38.400
Lakes, the Oral Roberts, and the Jack Coe's.

00:04:39.999 --> 00:04:49.320
But the Lord showed me, He said, "Brandon, we're going to see a new era of creative miracles that the world has never seen before.

00:04:49.320 --> 00:04:51.751
" Remember what I told you?

00:04:51.751 --> 00:05:01.531
I saw the chariots of fire all lined up in heaven, and they were all waiting for this great tidal wave that was coming on the earth.

00:05:01.531 --> 00:05:08.490
A massive tsunami wave of the glory of the Lord was coming on the earth.

00:05:08.490 --> 00:05:14.360
And I saw chariots of fire with packages all on the back of those chariots of fire.

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:28.639
And the Lord told me, He said, "During the Christmas time, I'm delivering those giftings into 2025 on the people who would receive them.

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:41.314
" Those chariots of fire were all around, and I could see them, and the packages were being delivered, and those are end-time giftings, and mantles were being delivered to the people.

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.564
It was a vision.

00:05:43.564 --> 00:05:53.520
But some of the gifts were not able to be delivered because the people weren't ready for them, and the chariot of fire went back up.

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:54.659
That was a sad time.

00:05:54.659 --> 00:05:59.550
I was thinking, "Oh goodness, but I wanted just to receive mine.

00:05:59.940 --> 00:06:01.080
" Do you understand?

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:06.220
And there were literally thousands of chariots, and they were all bringing the giftings.

00:06:06.220 --> 00:06:09.120
And the Lord told me, He said, "This is for the end times, Brandon.

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:17.394
" So those giftings are there, and that's what we're about to see: things and creative miracles that we've never seen before.

00:06:20.759 --> 00:06:28.510
What happened in the tent revival of old and the great things Oral Roberts and all of them did, that's the old things.

00:06:28.510 --> 00:06:35.199
And the Lord said, "They barely touched a glass full of what I'm wanting to do in this end-time move.

00:06:35.199 --> 00:06:39.177
" And I saw a great well in Oral Roberts University.

00:06:39.177 --> 00:06:48.320
I saw a massive well, and everybody like Kenneth Hagin and these men of God were taking a cup and they were drinking out of that well.

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:56.160
And He said, "This next generation, this last generation, this last push will go, and they'll dip their whole body in it.

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:57.830
They're not just going to get a cup, Brandon.

00:06:57.830 --> 00:07:02.000
I'm going to take them to the deep parts of that well.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:07.840
For what's about to take place has never been seen before.

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:13.500
" We're all excited about the glory cloud, and we get excited about what we heard happened at Azusa Street.

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:15.862
But the Lord said to me, "That's old things, Brandon.

00:07:16.411 --> 00:07:23.440
Behold, I'm going to do something new, something that you've never seen before.

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:26.080
" He's multifaceted, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:31.480
We have not seen all the splendor of what God has for us.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:37.759
We've only seen little glimpses of what He's allowed for that season.

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:42.137
"Think bigger," is what the Lord told me to tell you all today.

00:07:42.137 --> 00:07:43.006
Think bigger.

00:07:43.006 --> 00:07:45.590
You need to believe for bigger.

00:07:45.590 --> 00:08:06.639
What is it to you when I told you the scripture that when Moses had so much overflow, and I had my wife read it, about so much overflow that Moses said there's not enough room in the storehouse to take any more blessing?

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:07.771
There's too much.

00:08:07.771 --> 00:08:09.610
We can't receive it all.

00:08:09.610 --> 00:08:16.389
And the Lord said, "Brandon, it's a type and shadow of what I'm going to do for you in these last days for My remnant.

00:08:16.389 --> 00:08:17.931
That it'll be too much.

00:08:17.931 --> 00:08:20.549
There's not room enough to receive it all.

00:08:20.549 --> 00:08:26.160
" But not only that, they left healed, and there wasn't a feeble one among them.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:34.200
And the Lord said, "Brandon, if I did it for the children of Israel leaving Egypt, I'll do it for My bride that's leaving this earth.

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:37.848
" Do you understand what I'm about to do in this earth?

00:08:37.848 --> 00:08:43.108
In this last generation, there will be no feeble among you.

00:08:43.108 --> 00:08:44.056
Do you understand?

00:08:44.056 --> 00:08:46.160
There's not going to be any sick people.

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:52.577
You will have to resist healing: "I don't want to be healed, Lord.

00:08:52.577 --> 00:09:00.000
" He said, "I'm going to pour it out upon all flesh, Brandon, if you just believe me for it.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:09.040
With simple faith, what seemed to be the impossible will become possible if you just believe him for it.

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:12.343
So, I'm here to tell you today, yes, there's a great shaking.

00:09:12.343 --> 00:09:24.699
But people say, 'How can these things be, Brandon, if you're telling us all these dark things are coming and all this disruption and all the social unrest and all the sad days, the plague and all this stuff?

00:09:24.699 --> 00:09:30.731
' He said, 'Arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen on you, ladies and gentlemen.

00:09:30.731 --> 00:09:32.720
' And he said, 'Brandon, it will be like a quarter.

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.390
' I've told you this so many times.

00:09:34.390 --> 00:09:38.560
He said, 'It will be like a quarter.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:41.040
It'll be that thin.

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:50.040
You can either look on the dark, for the dark will get darker, but the light is going to be on the other side, and the light will be lighter and lighter.

00:09:50.600 --> 00:09:55.520
It'll be so dark in the world, Brandon, just like it was in Egypt.

00:09:55.520 --> 00:09:59.760
It'll be so dark, it'll be tangible.

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.120
Do you understand?

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:02.320
That's what I'm trying to say.

00:10:02.320 --> 00:10:06.480
It'll be tangible darkness like it was in Egypt.

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:15.680
But just across the street, there was glory and there was light on God's people.

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:25.531
' The Lord said to me, he said, "Brandon, that's how much it's going to be like now—a type and shadow again of great darkness on the earth, and it will be tangible.

00:10:25.863 --> 00:10:33.060
You're going to turn on the news and you're going to go, 'Oh my gosh, the sky is falling, Chicken Little!

00:10:33.060 --> 00:10:37.1000
' Or you can look at what's going on in the church and say, 'Whoa, the glory's happening, Jesus!

00:10:37.1000 --> 00:10:41.040
' Do you understand?

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.408
It will be that thin of a line.

00:10:43.408 --> 00:10:47.291
You can either go vertical or you can go horizontal.

00:10:47.291 --> 00:10:59.886
" And I said, "If you keep your eyes on what's going on in the news every day for what's coming, ladies and gentlemen, men's hearts will fail them for fear, looking after those things that are coming on the earth.

00:10:59.886 --> 00:11:05.048
" And people are going to be freaked out with the volcanoes, the earthquakes, the war, the rumors of war.

00:11:05.430 --> 00:11:16.228
Or you can focus on the brush arbor churches, you can focus on the limbs growing out and people getting delivered and healed and baptized in the Holy Ghost and the fire and deliverance.

00:11:16.228 --> 00:11:24.608
He told me, he said, 'The glory of the Lord is coming on people so much so that it will be like Moses, that the glory will shine on their faces.

00:11:24.608 --> 00:11:34.971
' I've seen certain ministers preaching and the glory, the Shekinah glory was radiating on their faces, and they were changed from glory to glory.

00:11:34.971 --> 00:11:42.080
That's why I tried to tell you all to sing that song all the time: 'From glory to glory, he's changing us.

00:11:42.080 --> 00:11:46.240
' It's a change from the inside out.

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:51.760
And he told me, he said, "Brandon, I'm going to show up on people's faces.

00:11:51.760 --> 00:11:59.360
You'll speak to your hand and manifestations will come like Elijah and Elisha.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:01.360
" Do you understand?

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:08.550
If they did it in the past, I'm going to do it in the future with greater works.

00:12:08.560 --> 00:12:10.900
The raven came and fed them.

00:12:10.900 --> 00:12:20.560
Think about what they had and what he did for them: the cloud the size of a man's hand, and then the sound of abundance of rain.

00:12:20.560 --> 00:12:22.746
"Can these bones live?

00:12:22.746 --> 00:12:25.211
" He says, "Brandon, can these bones live?

00:12:25.211 --> 00:12:28.800
" I said, "Yes, Father, they're spiritually dead.

00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:30.376
" People go, "Was that physically dead?

00:12:30.376 --> 00:12:31.622
" I believe both.

00:12:31.622 --> 00:12:32.605
Why not?

00:12:32.605 --> 00:12:35.819
Why not believe that the dead's going to rise?

00:12:35.819 --> 00:12:41.394
Why not believe that—I mean, that's the major miracle that we're wanting to see, folks.

00:12:41.394 --> 00:12:42.674
I'm hearing about it.

00:12:42.674 --> 00:12:45.902
It happens overseas, but have we seen it in America?

00:12:45.902 --> 00:12:48.523
Not very often, if at all.

00:12:48.523 --> 00:12:59.509
It might happen every once in a while and the news gets all over: 'This guy was dead for eight hours and he came back,' like this guy right here.

00:12:59.519 --> 00:13:01.059
It's going to happen all the time.

00:13:01.059 --> 00:13:02.986
Why can't it be the status quo?

00:13:02.986 --> 00:13:07.040
Why can't it be the norm to raise the dead?

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:11.326
Why does it have to be the abnormal that we never hear about it?

00:13:11.326 --> 00:13:18.160
We never see people's arms growing out and legs growing out and eyes coming back when they don't have any eyes.

00:13:18.160 --> 00:13:22.686
The things that seem impossible should be the norm.

00:13:22.686 --> 00:13:26.800
It shouldn't be abnormal to see people healed.

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:29.851
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory.

00:13:29.851 --> 00:13:31.540
And that's what I've tried to tell...

00:13:31.720 --> 00:13:35.760
I go over it and over and I said, "What are we missing?

00:13:35.760 --> 00:13:36.926
" You become sick.

00:13:36.926 --> 00:13:40.400
He says, "By his stripes ye are healed.

00:13:40.400 --> 00:13:42.093
" It's already done.

00:13:42.093 --> 00:13:45.760
It shouldn't be abnormal.

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:51.200
Well, we saw one get healed of, you know, she stubbed her toe and she was able to walk out.

00:13:51.200 --> 00:14:02.240
I want something that's so that no man can take and say that it wasn't God—somebody getting up from the dead.

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:05.908
Nobody's going to be able to say, "Well, Brother Brandon had the anointing.

00:14:05.908 --> 00:14:10.480
" No, God gets all the glory every time.

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:12.520
It should be that way.

00:14:12.520 --> 00:14:17.760
He is able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:14:17.760 --> 00:14:19.710
And aren't you ready to see that?

00:14:19.710 --> 00:14:21.760
And that's what I'm praying over.

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:24.720
And that's why I say this is the positive side of it.

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:34.240
I tell you the negative side and I try to come back with the reinforcements of telling you the positive side and say there's hope.

00:14:34.240 --> 00:14:40.159
Jesus has a plan and he wants to do something huge in every one of your lives.

00:14:40.159 --> 00:14:47.920
But it's time for us to walk in holiness and repentance and come back to the Father's heart.

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:50.120
What's on the Father's heart?

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:53.808
Being excited about what God's called us to do in these last days.

00:14:53.808 --> 00:14:58.948
So I want you to hear this prophetic word by Brother Kenneth E.

00:14:58.948 --> 00:15:01.930
Hagin from the 1980s.

00:15:01.930 --> 00:15:08.103
And this is an end-time vision that he had about what's coming.

00:15:08.103 --> 00:15:10.099
And this was back 40 years ago.

00:15:10.099 --> 00:15:12.114
So here's Diana and she's going to read this to you.

00:15:12.114 --> 00:15:13.085
She's been behind the camera.

00:15:13.085 --> 00:15:15.709
She said, "I'm embarrassed because I don't have my hair done.

00:15:15.709 --> 00:15:17.659
" She had a baseball cap on today.

00:15:18.079 --> 00:15:18.840
I said, "I don't care, baby.

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:20.674
You look good all the time.

00:15:20.674 --> 00:15:21.749
" "Thank you.

00:15:21.749 --> 00:15:22.286
" "Okay.

00:15:22.823 --> 00:15:24.148
Flowing in the supernatural.

00:15:24.411 --> 00:15:26.159
" This is by Kenneth E.

00:15:26.159 --> 00:15:27.120
Hagin from 1980.

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:38.971
"You are right on the verge—this is the prophecy through him—you are right on the verge, right on the verge of the greatest move and manifestation of the Spirit of God that this world has ever seen.

00:15:38.971 --> 00:15:44.820
You're right on the edge of it, like standing on the creek bank about to jump in.

00:15:44.820 --> 00:16:03.933
And if you'll give the more earnest heed unto things which you have heard—not only those things that you've heard about faith and those things that you've heard about healing, but also those things which you have heard about the Holy Spirit and the things that you've heard about angels and the things that you've heard about divine visitation.

00:16:04.426 --> 00:16:21.176
For remember that it was prophesied of Joel of old that, 'In the last days, saith the Lord, I will pour out my Spirit upon all flesh, and your young men shall see visions, and your old men shall dream dreams, and upon my handmaidens will I pour out my Spirit, and they will prophesy.

00:16:21.176 --> 00:16:22.346
' Oh, thank you, Lord.

00:16:22.346 --> 00:16:27.497
So, not only will it be that the young men will prophesy, but the young women will prophesy.

00:16:27.497 --> 00:16:33.566
And the anointing and the outflow of the Spirit of God shall be great and amazing in those days.

00:16:33.566 --> 00:16:36.607
For there shall be a visitation of angels, manifestations of angels.

00:16:38.205 --> 00:16:39.097
Expect it.

00:16:39.097 --> 00:16:45.577
Now, we don't worship angels, but they are ministering spirits sent forth to the heirs of salvation.

00:16:45.577 --> 00:16:47.970
So, God's going to bring them to help us.

00:16:47.970 --> 00:16:55.359
And he already told me it'll be two per unsaved person on the earth, to bring forth a...

00:16:55.359 --> 00:17:02.560
so that they'll be able to think clearly to make a decision without demonic influence.

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:02.907
Hallelujah.

00:17:02.907 --> 00:17:17.089
Even whatever he said when the Lord told us, Diana, he said, 'You'll start walking in places and the glory of the Lord is on your family, and devils will start to manifest around you and you'll cast the devil out of them.

00:17:17.089 --> 00:17:20.293
' Yes.

00:17:20.293 --> 00:17:21.280
Praise God.

00:17:21.280 --> 00:17:23.519
It's time to walk in it.

00:17:23.519 --> 00:17:24.149
Yes.

00:17:24.149 --> 00:17:30.809
Be not afraid, but yet take heed even in these areas, for Satan himself has at times come as an angel of light.

00:17:30.809 --> 00:17:36.480
But examine things in the light of Scriptures and walk in the light of the Word of God.

00:17:41.827 --> 00:17:48.480
And sometimes the angel will give you direction, even in your finances, and direction that would save your life.

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:48.995
" Okay.

00:18:05.067 --> 00:18:05.413
So, what was that?

00:18:05.413 --> 00:18:06.800
Read that again.

00:18:06.800 --> 00:18:11.269
I don't remember that.

00:18:16.662 --> 00:18:32.319
And sometimes the angel will give you direction, even in your finances, and the direction that would save your life, as in the case of the shipwreck of Paul, and direction concerning ministry, as the salvation of Cornelius and his household, and Philip as the angel spoke to him to go down to Gaza and the Ethiopian was converted.

00:18:37.760 --> 00:18:38.080
And so in these days there shall come a mighty manifestation of the Spirit.

00:18:38.080 --> 00:18:43.786
And the work that God intended should be done in these last days shall be accomplished.

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:47.280
For the time is short and things must be speeded up.

00:18:47.280 --> 00:18:50.470
And you'll learn much faster spiritual things than those of yesteryear.

00:18:50.470 --> 00:18:51.760
And you'll develop much faster.

00:18:51.760 --> 00:18:55.488
And it'll be said of some that they just virtually matured overnight.

00:19:10.906 --> 00:19:11.253
And they shall go forth and speak in the name of the Lord because they understood the principle of faith.

00:19:11.253 --> 00:19:14.103
They'll understand the principles of the kingdom.

00:19:14.469 --> 00:19:19.150
